total number of marks is 50 and the passing marks is 20
before runing the remedial.py install all the packages

win+R
type cmd
Ensure you have pip and python installed.
pip install pandas scikit-learn
pip install openpyxl


Remedial Dataset.xlsx this file is used for training the modal
    for Decision Tree model => DecisionTreeClassifier is used from sklearn packages
    for Naive Bayes model => GaussianNB is used from sklearn packages


test-remedial.xlsx this file is used for prediction of the students you can enter your own data for prediction
    if the prediction of the model is '1' then the student is slow lerner
    if the prediction of the model is '0' then the student is not a slow lerner